<p>The <em>adapted, translated (english) and corrected</em> pseudocode of algorithm is following</p>
<pre><code>function [Q, R] = divide(a, b)
    Q := 0
    R := a
    for i = n-1 → 0
        if a(n-1:i) &gt;= b
            Q(i) = 1
            a(n-1:1) = a(n-1:i) - b
        end
    end
    return [Q, R]
fin
</code></pre>
<p>Remark: actual algorithm is false. That is the reason a test a correct algorithm in C#</p>
<p>His implementation in <code>C#</code> using <code>UInt32_Register</code> class is following</p>
<pre class="lang-cs prettyprint-override"><code>static Tuple&lt;UInt32, UInt32&gt; Div(UInt32 N, UInt32 D)
{
    int n = 8 * sizeof(UInt32);
    UInt32_Register Q = 0; // QUOTIENT de la division
    UInt32_Register R = N; // RESTE de la division

    for (int i=n-1; i &gt;= 0; i--)
    {
        if (R[n-1,i] &gt;= D)
        {
            Q[i] = 1;
            R[n-1,i] = R[n-1,i] - D;
        }
    }
    return Tuple.Create((UInt32)Q, (UInt32)R);
}
</code></pre>
<p>A better implementation of this algorithm would be</p>
<pre class="lang-cs prettyprint-override"><code>static Tuple&lt;UInt32, UInt32&gt; Div(UInt32 N, UInt32 D)
{
    int n = 8 * sizeof(UInt32);
    UInt32_Register Q = 0; // QUOTIENT de la division
    UInt32          R = N; // RESTE de la division

    for (int i = n-1; i &gt;= 0; i--)
    {
        if ((R &gt;&gt; i) &gt;= D)
        {
            Q[i] = 1;
            R = R - (D &lt;&lt; i);
        }
    }
    return Tuple.Create((UInt32)Q, (UInt32)R);
}
</code></pre>
<p>To test this code, I use folloging <code>C#</code> code</p>
<pre class="lang-cs prettyprint-override"><code>    TestDiv(75, 10);
    TestDiv(12345678,10);
    TestDiv(8192, 4);
    TestDiv(8199, 4);
    TestDiv(8199, 5);

    static void TestDiv(UInt32 N, UInt32 D)
    {
        Console.WriteLine(N.ToString() + &quot;:&quot; + D.ToString());

        Tuple&lt;UInt32, UInt32&gt; t32 = EuclidianDiv(N, D);

        Console.WriteLine(&quot;    Q: &quot; + t32.Item1.ToString());
        Console.WriteLine(&quot;    R: &quot; + t32.Item2.ToString());

        if (t32.Item1 != N/D) Console.WriteLine(&quot;!&gt; Division ERROR&quot;);
        if (t32.Item2 != N%D) Console.WriteLine(&quot;!&gt; Modulo ERROR&quot;);
    }
</code></pre>
